- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper presents a method to model battery degradation and use it in optimal control formulations for power systems. This falls under the scope of systems and control.
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies): The paper deals with battery technologies and their degradation, which can be considered an emerging technology.
- cs.EE (Electrical Engineering): The paper discusses battery degradation in the context of power systems, which is a topic within electrical engineering.
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science): The paper presents a computational method to model battery degradation and use it in power system simulations, which falls under the scope of computational engineering.
- cs.OH (Other Computer Science): This paper could also be classified under "Other Computer Science" as it deals with a cross-disciplinary topic that does not fit neatly into any specific sub-category.
